entries.s_10: Ah, yes. A contact of mine mentioned that he was smug...er...shipping some rather odd items from a group that he couldn't name.
entries.s_12: Doesn't that kind of...shipping happen often?
entries.s_14: Yes. But he was visibly sweating, which is very odd. He's scared and in my experience, that's bad. Extremely bad. I've also lost track of him.
entries.s_16: I'll look for him. What can you tell me about him?
entries.s_18: His name is Moril. He's a Bothan who does some work for the traitorous CorSec troops. They may have information about where he is.
entries.s_24: I don't know you. I'm sorry, but I'm very busy.
entries.s_25: I've told you all that I can. Good luck!
entries.s_8: I'm following up on rumors for Lt. Joth.
